Jean Paul Gaultier Classique Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.3510

For the woman who celebrates her independence from the shackles of the world Jean Paul Gaultier presents Classique a luxury fragrance that allows her to wallow in the splendour of being a woman. As she lives through the saga of her life her strength of mind guarantees her every triumph and this Eau de Toilette celebrates each of her victories with elan. As peace floods her heart her senses fill with the sweet flirtations of the fragrance reminding her yet again of who she is supposed to be.

The iridescent aroma was introduced in September 2008; with opening notes of seductive rose and anise the femininity in you embraces Jean Paul Gaultier Classique as it mellows down to playful orange blossom and spicy ginger in the heart. Soft mellow vanilla and contrasting hot amber sends the senses into a catspin in the dry down. Flirty and independent the fragrance adds spice to the nice one’s life.

The one-of-a-kind bottle which resembles a statuette which has been inspired by the haute couture collection “Les Madone” incorporates the shapely nuances of the feminine form. The gold accents which spell luxury color your life with light of glamor.

Jean Paul Gaultier Classiqe Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.3510

Her chiselled features are the envy of women and her witty banter is the key to your heart. With her head firm on her shoulders and a wardrobe to boot she’s the toast of the town. Wherever she goes admirers crowd for a glimpse but they have to settle for a twinkle of the eye a coy smile and a trail of Jean Paul Gaultier Classique. Created by esteemed perfumer Jacques Cavallier this intoxicating Eau De Toilette is made for the quintessentially French house of Jean Paul Gaultier.

With pleasing sweet notes of star anise joining hands with delectably feminine extracts of rose the top note instantly attracts your attention. Moving into the heart note you can take in the buoyant contrast of fresh floral hints of orange blossom and the vibrant zest of ginger. Trailing off with a base note of creamy rich vanilla with smoky and resinous amber this decadent combination lulls you into a trance. Wear this entrancing fragrance at any time of the day to add a classic yet chic touch. This luxury perfume comes in a meticulously sculpted flacon which flaunt the sensuous curves of the female form. The simple bodice-like decoration on this flacon subtly channels the idea of the perfume’s aroma being the base of your beauty regime. Glowing in a nude hue reminiscent of youthful and blemish-free skin this perfume radiates a scintillating and luscious aura. A spritz of Classique and mesmerise the town with your delicate charm.
